replace into broadcast_text (entry, Male_Text) values (@magic_number, 'Why hello there, and welcome to the festivities. I apologize for the other guests not treating you with proper decency, it would appear they are quite ravenous these days.$B$B I am Lord Ebonlocke of Darkshire. I traveled here on my own accord and have not returned home since. I am quite aware of my current state in the tower, for I have been dead for some time. Most others that linger here are not as keen unfortunately. It would appear that I am stuck to haunt these halls until something most fortunate would happen to free me from this eternal confinement.$B$B Perhaps we can help one another, I have come to learn a few things, and meet others in my own situation during the time I have had in this tower.');
